cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the intersection of art and artificial intelligence, with a focus on making AI more transparent and understandable to humans. This falls under the category of AI (cs.AI) as well as human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and social implications (cs.CY) of AI. Finally, the paper discusses the potential for new configurations of humans and algorithms, which could fall under the category of social computing (cs.SI).
